Watch: Shilpa Shetty’s nagin dance after she had two sips of bhang on Holi 
18-3-2017 
Bhang, the traditional drink for Holi revelries, can do wonders to your dancing skills. And if we are talking about Bollywood actor Shilpa Shetty, it only adds a touch of madness to her talent. In a hilarious video her husband Raj Kundra shared on social media, Shilpa can been seen performing “naagin dance” with a friend.

Raj shared the video on Instagram on Monday and wrote, “The 2 sips of bhaaang effect!!! Hahaha @rohiniyer @officialshilpashetty #HoliWeekend #happyholi”

The 2 sips of bhaaang effect!!! Hahaha @rohiniyer @officialshilpashetty #HoliWeekend #happyholi A post shared by Raj Kundra (@rajkundra9) on Mar 13, 2017 at 1:09am PDT

The video is going viral and more than 27 thousand people have already watched it.

Shilpa was reportedly celebrating the festival in Lonavala with her family and friends.

